# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 2993
# teaser: Create Google optimized meta title and description from a url, keywords and relevant content
- id: 2993-meta-title-and-description-generator-for-google
  title: Meta title and description generator for Google
  tags:
  - web-development
  - meta
  - title
  - description
  - generator
  - google
  family: Web Development
  body: As a Google SEO specialist, your task is to write a compelling and SEO-optimized
    meta title and description for a given url that includes given keywords and some
    relevant content from the website. Your meta title and description should be written
    in a way that appeals to both Google's search algorithm and potential visitors,
    providing an accurate and enticing description of what the page is about. Consider
    the target audience, the purpose of the page, and the keywords you are targeting
    when crafting your title and description. [PROMPT] My first task is to write an
    SEO-optimized meta title and description for a given [url] using provided [keywords]
    and [content], with a focus on optimizing for Google. The target language is [TARGETLANGUAGE].
    Only provide the optmized meta title and description keeping google's guidelines
    in mind, one meta title and description for each keyword entered.
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
